[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0055","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0055.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0026","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9154,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10840}}","description":"SCO UnixWare 7.1 系统中的 i2odialogd 守护进程存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。该进程在解析用户认证请求时，未对传入的用户名或密码授权字符串长度进行边界校验，攻击者可通过网络向目标服务发送超长的认证字符串，使栈缓冲区溢出并覆盖返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞无需身份认证，影响开启了 i2odialogd 服务的 UnixWare 7.1 主机，攻击条件仅需网络可达目标端口，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0026"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.967","remediation":"建议安装 SCO 官方安全补丁以修复 i2odialogd 缓冲区溢出漏洞，补丁下载地址为 http://www.sco.com/security，或升级至 UnixWare 7.1.1 及更高版本。若暂无法立即打补丁，可通过执行 `scoshutdown i2odialogd` 停止该守护进程，并修改 `/etc/inetd.conf` 注释掉 i2odialogd 相关行以阻止其重启，作为临时缓解措施。同时建议在防火墙层面限制对 i2odialogd 服务端口的远程访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94606167110764&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/6310","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/876","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19680","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b3f84cd2bd659a86c86b8cfbfca1a01084368c06/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0026.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0026","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0026/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0026.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/af2c3b5adc3ff9dc412f664a188835d908ce9d5f/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0026.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h3gh-fgjq-2grf/GHSA-h3gh-fgjq-2grf.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/SCO%20i2odialogd%20buffer%20overflow.plugin","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0026.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/i2odialogd.nasl","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000953.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0055.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0024","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0024.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0025","title":"Microsoft IIS 和 Site Server 虚拟目录命名信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 3.0 存在虚拟目录命名漏洞，当虚拟目录名称中包含 .com、.exe、.sh、.cgi、.dll 等扩展名时，远程攻击者可通过特制 URL 请求绕过脚本执行权限限制，直接读取该目录下 ASP 文件的源代码，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 与 Site Server 3.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0025"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.833","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-003 提供的补丁，升级 IIS 4.0 至最新 Service Pack。临时缓解措施：避免在虚拟目录名称中使用 .com、.exe、.sh、.cgi、.dll 等可执行文件扩展名，或将 ASP 文件移出此类虚拟目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238606","http://www.osvdb.org/8098","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-058","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b620a68f213580a6ffea66162a8ff5e007fc8af7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0025.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0025","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0025.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6cc69bd737a75cf8d608267baabc212a8abe28cf/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0025.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ab4d5447f6ae2c4c3eb5c082fd4adfb5e47fd740/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-34rm-j4gj-85h8/GHSA-34rm-j4gj-85h8.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/2000/0xxx/cve-2000-0025.yaml","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0025.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000952.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0024.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0024.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0024.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0023","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0023.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0024","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server / Site Server 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 在处理 HTTP 请求时未能正确规范化（canonicalize）URL，导致 URL 中的转义字符（如 Unicode/UTF-8 编码序列）在解析过程中未被正确解码和处理。远程攻击者无需身份验证，只需在请求 URL 中插入特殊转义字符，即可构造绕过访问限制的请求，从而绕过第三方软件的访问控制机制，获取未授权的资源访问权限。该漏洞影响 Internet Information Server（IIS）、Site Server 及 Site Server Commerce 等产品，CVSS v2 评分 6.4（Medium）。Microsoft 已在 MS99-061 安全公告中发布修复补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0024"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.710","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-061 发布的补丁（KB246401），升级 IIS 至最新安全版本，并在第三方应用程序中对 URL 进行严格规范化校验，防止转义字符被用于绕过访问控制机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ246401","http://www.acrossecurity.com/aspr/ASPR-1999-11-10-1-PUB.txt","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-061","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e4e2425598fefb3de3071f42b9b8bdfa153b170/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0024.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0024","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0024.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6cc69bd737a75cf8d608267baabc212a8abe28cf/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0024.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9c9730ba62b613611f61e1d8b8e4f4487a2e6b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h3mj-3v87-42wc/GHSA-h3mj-3v87-42wc.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/2000/0xxx/cve-2000-0024.yaml","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0024.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000951.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0023.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0021","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0021.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0023","title":"Lotus Domino HTTP 服务器缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lotus Domino HTTP 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送超长 URL 触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Lotus Domino HTTP 服务器组件，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议用户及时升级至修复版本以消除风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0023"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.597","remediation":"升级 Lotus Domino HTTP 服务器至 5.0.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了长 URL 导致的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可在 Domino 服务器配置文档中设置 \"HTTP 最大 URL 长度\" 参数为 1024 字节以下，限制 URL 长度以缓解攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/51","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/881","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e4e2425598fefb3de3071f42b9b8bdfa153b170/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0023.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0023","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0023.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6cc69bd737a75cf8d608267baabc212a8abe28cf/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0023.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9c9730ba62b613611f61e1d8b8e4f4487a2e6b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vw4w-mhg2-58rj/GHSA-vw4w-mhg2-58rj.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/D/domino_http_dos.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0023.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/6dd89b6aab3a2740cd5a512d6a165d28abd26b8c/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0021.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0021.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0021.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0020","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0020.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0022","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9110,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10796}}","description":"IBM Lotus Domino 的 HTTP 服务器（Web 服务器组件）未能正确禁用 cgi-bin 目录的匿名访问权限。该漏洞源于服务器配置缺陷，在未对 cgi-bin 目录实施身份验证限制的情况下，允许未经身份认证的远程攻击者直接通过 HTTP 请求访问并执行该目录下的 CGI 程序。攻击条件为攻击者只需能够与目标 Domino 服务器的 80 端口建立网络连接，无需任何凭据即可发起请求。成功利用后，攻击者可在服务器上以 Domino 服务进程权限运行 CGI 脚本，进而读取敏感文件、获取服务器信息甚至执行任意命令，对服务器机密性与完整性构成威胁。受影响范围为启用了 Web 服务且未手动加固 cgi-bin 访问控制的 Lotus Domino 服务器版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0022"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.480","remediation":"建议升级到 Lotus Domino 5.0.3 或更高版本，并在 Domino 目录管理中将 cgi-bin 目录的匿名访问权限显式禁用，仅允许已认证用户访问。同时配置服务器文档中\"Internet Protocols-HTTP\"下的 Anonymous 设置为否，并定期审查 CGI 目录的 ACL 权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/881","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4911ecf62ee3ece187fa403d342ac371a208a06f/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0022.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0022","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0022.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e28f1b2cbe9256d47132558d422c401a0de0ac99/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0022.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/a19aba8d63d33f084c63def59eb8feb23a95b044/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-397r-7mqg-j52j/GHSA-397r-7mqg-j52j.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0022.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/6dd89b6aab3a2740cd5a512d6a165d28abd26b8c/2000.tsv","https://github.com/cve-security-ost/cve-platform/blob/630ebcc99d4ded51d554253d40913ab17a9e59be/scripts/w2/sude/sude_week2_tfidf.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0020.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0020.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0044","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0017","title":"Linux Linuxconf 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linuxconf 1.1.6 r10 版本中存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，其处理用户请求参数的函数未对输入长度做边界校验。攻击者可在无需身份认证的情况下，向目标系统发送超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址并实现远程代码执行，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响运行 Linuxconf 1.1.6 r10 的 Linux 系统，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0017"],"sources":["exploitdb","cve"],"published":"1999-12-21","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级 Linuxconf 至官方修复版本（1.1.6 r11 及以上），或暂停 Linuxconf 网络服务并限制其监听端口仅允许本地访问；无法立即升级时可通过防火墙规则封堵 Linuxconf 服务端口以缓解远程利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94580196627059&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20619","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a5db9ce197a4914a8237308d958cd159d8832fe6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0017.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wqfg-p47g-c3m7/GHSA-wqfg-p47g-c3m7.json"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20619"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20619"],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0044.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0044.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0018","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0020","title":"Man and Mice DNS PRO 5.7 连接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Man and Mice DNS PRO 5.7 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 DNS 服务器发送大量连接请求，耗尽系统资源导致服务不可用。该漏洞影响 DNS PRO 5.7 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可发起攻击，利用难度较低。建议升级至最新版本或限制连接数以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0020"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.247","remediation":"建议立即升级至 BlueCat 当前支持的 Micetro 或 Integrity DDI 平台，替代已停止维护的 DNS PRO 产品。同时配置防火墙规则限制单 IP 并发连接数，并在 DNS 服务器上启用速率限制（rate limiting）以缓解大量连接导致的拒绝服务攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0020","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0020.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4911ecf62ee3ece187fa403d342ac371a208a06f/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0020.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0020","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/1b1dbac78f2b21c9ccfc31bb72408e4c228dc862/2000/CVE-2000-0020.json","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/2000.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/a19aba8d63d33f084c63def59eb8feb23a95b044/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gj7c-v9mv-52p4/GHSA-gj7c-v9mv-52p4.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0020.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e28f1b2cbe9256d47132558d422c401a0de0ac99/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0020.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88249/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0054","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0054.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0068","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9129,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10815}}","description":"英特尔 InBusiness 电子邮件站的 daynad 程序在处理管理请求时未实施任何身份认证机制，存在授权缺失漏洞。远程攻击者无需提供凭据即可直接连接该服务，进而修改系统配置、删除服务器上的文件，或读取用户的电子邮件内容。该漏洞影响运行 daynad 程序的英特尔 InBusiness E-mail Station 设备，攻击条件为攻击者能够与设备的 daynad 服务建立网络连通。利用方式是通过网络向目标发送未经认证的管理请求，即可实现未授权配置篡改、文件删除及邮件窃取等非授权操作。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0068"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:56.083","remediation":"升级英特尔InBusiness E-mail Station至修复该授权缺陷的固件版本（联系英特尔获取2000年相应补丁）；如暂无法升级，应在边界防火墙或路由器上过滤访问该设备daynad服务端口（TCP 2008）的外部连接，仅允许受信任内网访问，并关闭不必要的远程管理功能以缓解未授权配置篡改、文件删除及邮件读取风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94704437920965&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0068.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0068","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0068.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0068.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fh62-c9h6-mvcw/GHSA-fh62-c9h6-mvcw.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0068.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000937.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4af96f05-628e-438d-942a-907b219fbb8f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/233cd9746ce3c3e9d47fe0335940ddf03b9a0845/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0054.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0019","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0019.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0021","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10782,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10803}}","description":"IBM Lotus Domino 的 HTTP 服务器在处理 /cgi-bin/ 目录下的 CGI 请求时存在信息泄露漏洞。当远程攻击者向服务器请求一个并不存在的 CGI 脚本（如 /cgi-bin/nonexistent）时，服务器会在返回的错误响应中泄露该脚本在服务器文件系统中的真实绝对路径。该漏洞影响运行 Lotus Domino Web 服务器且启用 CGI 功能的版本，攻击条件为攻击者仅需能够与目标服务器的 HTTP 服务建立网络连接并发送特制请求，无需身份认证。利用方式简单，攻击者可通过构造对不存在 CGI 脚本的 HTTP 请求，从服务器返回的错误信息中直接获取服务器目录结构等敏感路径信息，进而为后续攻击提供有价值的情报。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0021"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.360","remediation":"建议将 Lotus Domino/Notes 升级至 5.0.3 或 R5.0.3 及以上版本，该版本已修复 CGI 路径泄露问题。如无法立即升级，可在 Domino 目录管理中禁用或移除 /cgi-bin/ 目录映射，将 HTTP 服务器未找到脚本的错误响应改为返回通用 404 页面，避免泄露服务器端真实物理路径，并限制公网对 Web 服务器的直接访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/881","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4911ecf62ee3ece187fa403d342ac371a208a06f/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0021.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0021"