Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94606572912422&w=2","http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9912&L=NTBUGTRAQ&P=R3556","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1ef693821096ed2e21366dae590c013e3dc540aa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0004.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0004","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0004.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cc528fa33408da88ea19cf3d01d2185cd0ffe95a/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0004.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x8rm-jcqv-qh7g/GHSA-x8rm-jcqv-qh7g.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88260/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0004.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-41.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--833b202d-5e55-4f68-85fa-788bff23a5c3.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0006.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0906","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0906.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0352","title":"University of Washington Pine URL 命令注入漏洞","description":"Pine 邮件客户端 4.21 版本之前存在 shell 元字符过滤漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向用户发送包含恶意 URL 的邮件，当用户点击该 URL 时，Pine 未能正确过滤其中的 shell 元字符，导致攻击者可以在目标系统上以用户权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Pine 4.21 之前的所有版本，无需身份认证即可触发，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0352"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:32.313","remediation":"升级至 Pine 4.21 或更高版本，该版本已修复 URL 中 shell 元字符的过滤逻辑。如无法升级，可禁用 Pine 的 URL 自动调用功能，或限制邮件客户端调用外部程序（如 web 浏览器）的权限，避免传递含特殊字符的 URL 给 shell 处理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/suse_security_announce_36.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/810","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.10.9911171818220.12375-100000%40ray.compu-aid.com","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0352.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0352.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0352","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0352.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0352.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/3a007c8fe94b232452ea95ec8ec071fdd18c286f/2000/CVE-2000-0352.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/a913ac9f87691de86825ecccd6699d1970d6fddc/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-03xx/CVE-2000-0352.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0352.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0352.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0352.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0906.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0060","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0060.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0073","title":"Microsoft Windows RTF解析器缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 系统中的 Rich Text Format (RTF) 阅读器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当用户使用受影响系统打开包含恶意构造控制词的特制 RTF 文件时，可触发缓冲区溢出，导致程序崩溃或拒绝服务。攻击者可通过诱使用户打开恶意 RTF 文件（如通过电子邮件附件或网页下载）来利用此漏洞。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98、NT 4.0 及终端服务器等多个版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0073"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-11-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:56.680","remediation":"受影响系统均为已停止支持的旧版 Windows（95/98/NT 4），微软未发布官方补丁。建议立即升级至 Windows 10/11 等受支持版本；在无法升级的环境中，配置组策略禁止从邮件客户端和浏览器自动打开 RTF 附件，并教育用户不打开来源不明的 .rtf 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ249973","http://xforce.iss.net/search.php3?type=2&pattern=win-malformed-rtf-control-word","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-005","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19633","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0073.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d25d3aeab9dc76030f155f9e202a4a7c294f86bf/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0073.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0073","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/2000.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0073.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0073.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hp77-39hv-xf39/GHSA-hp77-39hv-xf39.js