000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:29.370","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 6 及以上版本，或改用现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）；在 IE 中将 Internet 区域安全级别设为「高」并禁用 ActiveX 控件；在 Outlook 中阻止 CAB 附件执行，设置以纯文本阅读邮件。该漏洞源于 Windows 2000 之前版本，建议同步升级操作系统。当前这些版本均已停止支持，彻底修复需升级到受支持的操作系统和浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-048","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19603","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0329.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0329","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0329.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0329.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65p6-f2x3-5fgg/GHSA-65p6-f2x3-5fgg.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/bibliotxt/bibliotxt/blob/07bb3ac8e74e6f78514faabae1ce10b662cf48a1/zines/trenchcoat-diaries/tcpaper2.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0329.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0272.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0272.toml"],"has_poc":true,